{{Quote|I used to spend a fair amount of time in establishments much like this one, places like the Green Glowstone Tavern and the Dewback Inn, in the Zi-Kree sector on&mdash;|I-5YQ, to [[Den Dhur]]|<ref name="MedStar I">''[[MedStar I: Battle Surgeons]]''</ref>}}
The '''Green Glowstone Tavern''' was located near one end of the [[Crimson Corridor]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Lorn Pavan]] and [[I-5YQ]] often visited it, despite it officially not allowing [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. It had a [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] bartender.

